headline: The Number of Days You Need To Work To Afford a Monthly Mortgage Payment in Each State
summary: The median national home price in the U.S. is $412,000 and for Americans looking to buy a home, the magic number of days required to work per month to afford the mortgage payment is 10, according to Realtor.com® data. But, for residents in some states, the number of workdays required can go up to 17 days, a whole week more.

headline: DAZN secures control of News Corp's Foxtel as $2.1 billion deal goes through
summary: Rupert Murdoch's News Corp on Wednesday said it completed the sale of its Australian cable-TV business Foxtel to British-owned sports network DAZN in a A$3.4 billion ($2.14 billion) deal. ($1 = 1.5883 Australian dollars)

headline: News Corp Completes the Sale of Foxtel Group to DAZN
summary: SYDNEY, April 02, 2025--News Corporation ("News Corp" or the "Company") today announced it has completed the sale of Foxtel Group ("Foxtel") to DAZN Group Limited ("DAZN").
